## Module 3: RAG / AI

### 🟠 BUG-8: [rag-indexing.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/ndvng/Desktop/iwsFinal/studyVault-backend/src/modules/rag/services/rag-indexing.service.ts) — indexing loop không concurrent, rất chậm với document nhiều chunk

**File:** [rag-indexing.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/ndvng/Desktop/iwsFinal/studyVault-backend/src/modules/rag/services/rag-indexing.service.ts) — dòng 54-68

```ts
for (const chunk of chunks) {       // ← sequential
  const embeddingValues = await this.geminiService.createEmbedding(chunk.chunkText);
  // ...
  await this.chunkRepository.getRepository().save(chunk);
}
```

**Vấn đề:** 20 chunks = 20 sequential API calls. Nên dùng `Promise.all` với concurrency limit (ví dụ 3 concurrent).

---

### 🟡 BUG-9: [rag-summary.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/ndvng/Desktop/iwsFinal/studyVault-backend/src/modules/rag/services/rag-summary.service.ts) — [normalizeSummary](file:///c:/Users/ndvng/Desktop/iwsFinal/studyVault-backend/src/modules/rag/services/rag-summary.service.ts#368-417) không consistent: `body` là `null` hay `''`

**File:** [rag-summary.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/ndvng/Desktop/iwsFinal/studyVault-backend/src/modules/rag/services/rag-summary.service.ts) — dòng 414

```ts
return {
  // ...
  format: 'structured',
  body: null,    // ← null
};
```

Nhưng type `StructuredDocumentSummary.body` có thể là `string | null`. Frontend cần xử lý cả hai trường hợp `null` và `''`.

---

### 🟡 BUG-10: Vector search SQL hardcode `SOURCE_SNIPPET_LENGTH = 280` thay vì dùng parameterized

**File:** [rag-question-answering.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/ndvng/Desktop/iwsFinal/studyVault-backend/src/modules/rag/services/rag-question-answering.service.ts) — dòng 271

```ts
LEFT(c.chunk_text, ${SOURCE_SNIPPET_LENGTH}) AS "snippet",
```

String interpolation vào SQL — không nguy hiểm vì là constant number, nhưng không phải practice tốt.

